  "merger_description": "Sika AG proposes to acquire 100% of the equity in Akkim Yap\u0131 Kimyasallar\u0131 Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim \u015eirketi, Akfix Kimya Lojistik Hizmetleri Limited \u015eirketi, Akde Kimya Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim \u015eirketi, and Akkim Europe SRL (together, **Akkim**).\n\nSika AG is a globally active speciality chemicals group headquartered in Switzerland. Sika AG supplies chemical-based admixtures, mortars, sealants and adhesives, damping and reinforcing materials, structural strengthening systems, industrial flooring, as well as roofing and waterproofing systems. Their products are used in the building sector and by manufacturing industries.\n\nAkkim, founded in Turkey, is a chemical product manufacturer specialising in the manufacture of sealants, adhesives, PU foams, waterproofing products and aerosols. Akkim\u2019s main brand in Australia is Akfix.",
